{"tid":139792,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果放寬保養條款：搵人整 iPhone 芒唔再影響保養","createTime":"2017-03-01T16:42:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-01T17:57:14.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"64aa7ab267e31eff2beaf384df48defc8c46e2c0","tid":139792,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T16:42:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: violet;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>蘋果：找別人修 iPhone 螢幕不再影響保養<br />\n<a href=\"https://technews.tw/2017/03/01/third-party-iphone-screen-repairs-no-longer-void-warranty/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftechnews.tw%2F2017%2F03%2F01%2Fthird-party-iphone-screen-repairs-no-longer-void-warranty%2F&d=7O3ztiABqAoAY%2BrF22wgzdr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=ac14c08e\" target=\"_blank\">https://technews.tw/2017/03/01/third-party-iphone-screen-repairs-no-longer-void-warranty/</a></strong></div></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.technews.tw/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/14122228/iPhone-family-624x468.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.technews.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F11%2F14122228%2FiPhone-family-624x468.jpg&h=cd736108&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n蘋果最近發布一項新的產品保養政策，大開方便之門，只要不影響 iPhone 內部其他組件，由第三方進行螢幕更換與維修將不再影響 iPhone 的保養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n根據一份由蘋果發給蘋果官方零售店員工的內部備忘錄指出，未來經由第三方維修或更換 iPhone 螢幕，將不再影響 iPhone 原本的保養。不過這項新的保養政策還是保留了一些但書，如果這些第三方維修單位對除了螢幕以外的其他零件造成損傷，使用者仍需付擔全額的維修費用。<br />\n<br />\n在過去，iPhone 的螢幕維修一直是許多使用者心中的痛，特別是在 iPhone 6 開始改用弧面螢幕與圓弧邊框設計後，微微凸起的螢幕更容易發生碎裂問題，為了節省預算，許多人使用者紛紛求助第三方維修單位，選擇用較低的價格更換或維修螢幕。但是根據過去蘋果的保養政策，這樣的做法會直接令保養失效，後續再有任何問題，使用者都必須支付全額的維修費用。<br />\n<br />\n而現在，只要使用者手中的 iPhone 仍在保養期內，在不影響其他零件的情況下就可以放心進行螢幕的更換與維修，不過還是建議尋找有信譽的廠商或店家進行維修，一方面避免不熟悉的店家不小心損傷其他零件造成保養失效，一方面也比較安心。<br />\n<br />\n使用者在維修螢幕前，最好還是先向原本的保養提供商詢問相關事項，以免在不知情的情況下讓自己的權益受損。"},{"pid":"7e7eeebbb0d5945145830e236195164b0ba247e8","tid":139792,"uid":1367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T16:45:40.000Z","msg":"為iphone 7s新mon 鋪路"},{"pid":"7288ccba9521bb32092d4e4deb0d2f3564b6051e","tid":139792,"uid":1130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T16:47:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>為iphone 7s新mon 鋪路</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a078c074ce63d35975a936380a5157b6fdf15437","tid":139792,"uid":49,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T16:47:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a33ecdfe49547dd42a4307b26485a2e67daddc6c","tid":139792,"uid":7886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T17:57:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 終於有德政"}]}